    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ζηνὶ θ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">εῶ</supplied>ν π<supplied reason="lost">άντων<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> κρατοῦ</supplied>ντι Σαράπ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ιδι</supplied> Κάσ<supplied reason="lost">σ</supplied>ιος Αλ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low"> κατασκευ</supplied>ασθέν<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">τα ἐπὶ</supplied> ΑΙ<supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>ΛΑϹ<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> ἐπιτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ρόπου</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>7 Fragmente, wovon jeweils 3 aneinanderpassende zwei separate Gebilde (a u. c) gestalten. Ein kleines Fragment (b) bleibt. Tabula ansata. Fundstelle bezieht sich auf die neu gefundenen Fragmente.</p>
            </div>
